 the six segments from ''[[The Flintstone Comedy Show]]'' (two and/or three segments aired per half-hour episode). The segments included ''The Flintstone Family Adventures'', ''Bedrock Cops'', ''Pebbles, Dino and Bamm-Bamm'', ''Captain Caveman'', ''Dino and Cavemouse'' and ''The Frankenstones''.<ref>[https://books.google.ca/books?id=AKlgjBCPPnsC&pg=PA148&lpg=PA148&dq=the+flintstone+funnies&source=bl&ots=sA7VUMeQgz&sig=19KrBEe9OLmuwXRvvcyA953wvjA&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj4majvxcHYAhWl3YMKHQWCCvM4FBDoAQgsMAE#v=onepage&q=the%20flintstone%20funnies&f=false Encyclopedia of Television Series, Pilots and Specials 1974\u20131984, Volume 2], Terrace, Vincent (1985).</ref>\n\n==Episodes==\nFor episode titles and synopsis, see ''[[The Flintstone Comedy Show]]''\n\n==Voice cast==\n* [[Gay Autterson]] as [[Betty Rubble]], Wiggy Rockstone\n* [[Mel Blanc]] as [[Barney Rubble]], [[Captain Caveman and the Teen Angels|Captain Caveman]], [[Dino (The Flintstones)|Dino]]\n* [[Henry Corden]] as [[Fred Flintstone]]\n* [[Ruta Lee]] as [[The Frankenstones|Hidea Frankenstone]]\n* [[Kenneth Mars]] as Lou Granite\n* [[Mitzi McCall]] as Penny Pillar\n* [[Don Messick]] as Schleprock\n* [[Charles Nelson Reilly]] as [[The Frankenstones|Frank Frankenstone]]\n* [[Paul Reubens]] as [[The Frankenstones|Freaky Frankenstone]]\n* [[Zelda Rubinstein]] as [[The Frankenstones|Atrocia Frankenstone]]\n* [[Michael Sheehan (actor)|Michael Sheehan]] as [[Bamm-Bamm Rubble]]\n* [[John Stephenson (actor)|John Stephenson]] as Mr. Slate\n* [[Russi Taylor]] as [[Pebbles Flintstone]], Cavemouse\n* [[Jean Vander Pyl]] as [[Wilma Flintstone]]\n* [[Lennie Weinrib]] as Moonrock Crater, Sgt. Boulder\n* [[Frank Welker]] as [[Shmoo]], [[The Frankenstones|Rockjaw]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb title|0923172}}\n*[http://www.bcdb.com/cartoons/Hanna-Barbera_Studios/D-F/The_Flintstone_Funnies/ ''The Flintstone Funnies''] at the [[The Big Cartoon DataBase|Big Cartoon DataBase]]\n\n{{The Flintstones}}\